g: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.47; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">use another member's account, share an account with another member, or maintain more than one account.</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.2rem 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.47; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">create another account if we have already terminated your account, unless you have our permission.</li></ul><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Mego reserves the right to investigate and/or terminate your account without a refund of any purchases if you have violated this Agreement, misused the Service or behaved in a way that Mego regards as inappropriate or unlawful, including actions or communications that occur on or off the Service. In addition, in certain instances, we may terminate your account for violating the applicable terms of any of the Match Group family of businesses, which includes in addition to Mego, services such as OkCupid, Plenty of Fish, Match, Meetic, BlackPeopleMeet, LoveScout24, OurTime, Pairs, ParPerfeito, and Twoo (for more details, click&nbsp;<a href="https://mtch.com/safety" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--color--text-link,inherit); text-decoration-line: underline;">here</a>). In the event that you violate these rules or our Community Guidelines, your authorization to use the Service will be automatically revoked.</p></h1><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 1rem 0px 0.8rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">9. Other Members' Content.</h2><h1 class="headline" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.3rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;"><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Although Mego reserves the right to review and remove Content that violates this Agreement, such Content is the sole responsibility of the member who posts it, and Mego cannot guarantee that all Content will comply with this Agreement. If you see Content on the Service that violates this Agreement, please report it within the Service or via our&nbsp;<a href="https://www.help.Mego.com/hc/requests/new" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--color--text-link,inherit); text-decoration-line: underline;">contact form.</a></p></h1><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 1rem 0px 0.8rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">10. Purchases.</h2><h1 class="headline" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.3rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;"><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Generally.</span>&nbsp;From time to time, Mego may offer products and services for purchase ("in app purchases") through the App Store, Google Play Store, carrier billing, Mego direct billing or other payment platforms authorized by Mego. If you choose to make an in app purchase, you will be prompted to confirm your purchase with the applicable payment provider, and your method of payment (be it your card or a third party account such as the Google Play Store or App Store (your "Payment Method") will be charged for the in app purchase at the prices displayed to you for the service(s) you've selected as well as any sales or similar taxes that may be imposed on your payments, and you authorize Mego or the third party account, as applicable, to charge you.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Auto-Renewal; Automatic Card Payment</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">If you purchase an auto-recurring periodic subscription through an in app purchase, your Payment Method will continue to be billed for the subscription until you cancel. After your initial subscription commitment period, and again after any subsequent subscription period, your subscription will automatically continue for an additional equivalent period, at the price you agreed to when subscribing. Your card payment information will be stored and subsequently used for the automatic card payments in accordance with the Agreement.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Objections to a payment already made should be directed to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.help.Mego.com/hc/requests/new" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--color--text-link,inherit); text-decoration-line: underline;">Customer support</a>&nbsp;if you were billed directly by Mego or the relevant third party account such as the App Store. You are also able to object by contacting your bank or payment provider, who can provide further information on your rights as well as applicable time limits. You may unconditionally withdraw your consent to automatic card payments at any time by going to Settings on Mego or the relevant third party account, but be advised that you are still obligated to pay any outstanding amounts.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">If you want to change or terminate your subscription, you will need to log in to your third party account (or Settings on Mego, if applicable) and follow the instructions to terminate or cancel your subscription, even if you have otherwise deleted your account with us or if you have deleted the Mego application from your device.</span>&nbsp;Deleting your account on Mego or deleting the Mego application from your device does not terminate or cancel your subscription; Mego will retain all funds charged to your Payment Method until you terminate or cancel your subscription on Mego or the third party account, as applicable. If you terminate or cancel your subscription, you may use your subscription until the end of your then-current subscription term, and your subscription will not be renewed after your then-current term expires.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Additional Terms that apply if you pay Mego directly with your Payment Method.</span>&nbsp;If you pay Mego directly, Mego may correct any billing errors or mistakes that it makes even if it has already requested or received payment. If you initiate a chargeback or otherwise reverse a payment made with your Payment Method, Mego may terminate your account immediately in its sole discretion.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">You may edit your Payment Method information by visiting Mego and going to Settings. If a payment is not successfully settled, due to expiration, insufficient funds, or otherwise, and you do not edit your Payment Method information, terminate or cancel your subscription, you remain responsible for any uncollected amounts and authorize us to continue billing the Payment Method, as it may be updated. This may result in a change to your payment billing dates. In addition, you authorize us to obtain updated or replacement expiration dates and card numbers for your credit or debit card as provided by your credit or debit card issuer. The terms of your payment will be based on your Payment Method and may be determined by agreements between you and the financial institution, credit card issuer or other provider of your chosen Payment Method. If you reside outside of the Americas, you agree that your payment to Mego will be through MTCH Technology Services Limited.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antiali